Epic Mix - Anime

A branch of the EPIC MIX variety merges.

PERSONAL USE IS ALWAYS WELCOME - COMMERCIAL USE IS UP TO YOU BUT PLEASE RESPECT THE LISC OF EACH MODEL THAT WAS MERGED INTO THIS!

DIFFUSERS OPTION + CKPT OPTION IS LOCATED HERE: https://huggingface.co/Duskfallcrew/EpicMix_AniV2

BACKUPS USUALLY ARE HERE FOR PUBLIC MODELS: https://huggingface.co/Duskfallcrew

SUPPORT US:

WE ARE PROUDLY SPONSORED BY: https://www.piratediffusion.com/

If you got requests, or concerns, We're still looking for beta testers: JOIN THE DISCORD AND DEMAND THINGS OF US: https://discord.gg/Da7s8d3KJ7

Lora Request Form: https://forms.gle/NEkcMmVEjG4pBAP7A

JOIN OUR SUBREDDIT: https://www.reddit.com/r/earthndusk/

Listen to the music that we've made that goes with our art:
https://open.spotify.com/playlist/00R8x00YktB4u541imdSSf?si=b60d209385a74b38

We stream a lot of our testing on twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/duskfallcrew

Pre-Release Models, Lora Backups - Send us pizza! https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

STOP

We used AFTER DETAILER AND HI RES FIX.

Upscaler Choices:

https://huggingface.co/uwg/upscaler/tree/main/ESRGAN

Vae Alternatives:

https://huggingface.co/datasets/VASVASVAS/vae


Hi Res Fix: DO NOT USE WAIFUGAN 3000 or it just looks weird.

(We were testing random Upscalers lmao)

Submit SFW and amazing wallpapers at PaprGG: https://discord.gg/2UXkGwndVE

ANY V4 UPDATES THE MIX WILL BE ADDED TO THE "MODEL VERSION" cards, we're running out of room.

Why branched?

Two reasons: One - I can't edit the original anymore for some wild reason, and two - V4 is predominately MORE ANIME than the Alpha and beta up to v3.

If you want the original go here: https://civitai.com/models/20562/epic-mix-anime-realism-and-nsfw-support

if Civit goes down and you can download: https://huggingface.co/Duskfallcrew/Epicmix_v4

Other merges and backups (not always named the same):
https://huggingface.co/Duskfallcrew/EpicMix_Merges

That explains all the merges until NOW that is.

Epic MIX V4 merge combo includes:

V3 (V2 + Anything 3.0) + Pastel Boys and Pegasus 9 Mix

This was a step up because the original EPIC mix wasn't producing men very well, and well here ya go!

Our list of LORA AND EMBEDS are on the main model.

Sample prompts are in the image gens, maybe another time we'll focus better on sample prompts.
